This is a Chef-server & Chef-client example on vagrant.
==========================================================================

# Features
	1. make chef-server, chef-client
	2. make org, user, client, node
	3. get public cookbook, make custom cookbook
	4. upload cookbook and assign it to a node
	5. run chef-client

# Execution
	mkdir -p ~/tz-chef/client/chef-repo
	
	vagrant destroy -f && vagrant up
	
# Run
	https://192.168.82.170
	
	admin / admin123

